data.title: With a sense of profound joy and deep-rooted pride, we commemorated the 88th Fujitsu Foundation Day at our Chennai location. In the...
data.meta_description:
282 likes, 0 comments - fujitsu_india on August 10, 2023: "With a sense of profound joy and deep-rooted pride, we commemorated the 88th Fujitsu Foundation Day at our Chennai location. 

In the presence of esteemed leaders, dedicated team members, and their families, an atmosphere of spirited enthusiasm and camaraderie flourished.

The stage was graced by the captivating performances of renowned dance troupes from diverse regions, a symphony of vibrant colors and dynamic rhythms reflecting the tapestry of India's rich cultural heritage.

Our rewards & recognitions ceremony stood as a testament to the work conducted by individuals and team award recipients who have been instrumental in shaping the trajectory of Fujitsu's growth story. Their dedication and contribution have been pivotal in our continuous pursuit of excellence.

Our heartfelt appreciation extends to our esteemed customers, trusted partners, and the local communities that form the pillars of our success. We recognize the unyielding support of our current and former team members, whose unwavering commitment has been pivotal in charting Fujitsu's journey to its present stature.

#CelebratingSuccess #FujitsuGrowthJourney #ProudMoments #88Yearsoflegacy".
